{"tid":1660412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2007張家輝電影《出埃及記》教會大家嘅事","createTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T13:26:35.000Z","uid":77905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d29874e44b6d8ba453df6ef1c9034baace8f24","tid":1660412,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:05.000Z","msg":"自小就聽過一個故事，有犯人被捕後帶到警署，突然有一批赤裸裸上身，只穿內褲和蛙鞋，面帶潛水眼罩的人出現，把犯人痛打一頓。<br />\n這個小故事，是家中一名當警察的長輩，在飯桌分享的都市傳說。<br />\n「警察打犯一直都有，俾人打嘅犯投訴都無用，因為根本無人信。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wwIbZ3A4OWs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwwIbZ3A4OWs&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=fdf3f491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wwIbZ3A4OWs</a><br />\n<br />\n「原來有啲事，荒謬到一個程度，就唔會有人相信」<br />\n「有啲嘢好大，係你理唔嚟，唔好忘記自己係邊個。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A6%AE%E5%B4%A9%E6%A8%82%E5%A3%9E-%E8%8E%AB%E9%81%8E%E6%96%BC%E6%AD%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A3%259E-%25E8%258E%25AB%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%25AD%25A4%2F&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=125f503d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A3%259E-%25E8%258E%25AB%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%25AD%25A4%2F&h=b026c0d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A6%AE%E5%B4%A9%E6%A8%82%E5%A3%9E-%E8%8E%AB%E9%81%8E%E6%96%BC%E6%AD%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"b217a8cc5f61cd37b5eeedd47865c1ab38880b38","tid":1660412,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SI